# Its election time in Pakistan: Go rich boy, go! — Jay Haque, 2013 (ASL 540)
# No published walkthrough exists — derived from game source (game.aslx).
# Satirical election-day gamebook (`_editorstyle=gamebook`): commands are page
# names. The source contains ZERO finish() calls and NO option-less reachable
# page — every ending page only offers "Play the game from the start!" — so the
# script parks on the ending page WITHOUT restarting; state=Running there is
# the game's complete ending (cf. the other gamebook rows).
# Chosen arc (the score ending): take crush Aaliya to vote (lie to mom, tell
# Aaliya to sneak out), survive the registration mix-up and the drive to
# Murdabad (hard left = "Score +500 for taking a wide turn"), thread the rat
# maze straight-straight-straight, vote for Imran Khan, and truthfully tell
# Aaliya — she drags you into an empty room and kisses you: "You SCORE
# +20,000 for getting the girl!" (Page119). Dead pages 9/11/12/59/63/69/134
# are unreferenced in the release. No RNG/timers.
